## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7fdb1-325"><xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignSurface.BeginLoad%2A>必须事先启动加载过程调用方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fdb1-325">The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignSurface.BeginLoad%2A> method must be called beforehand to start the loading process.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fdb1-326">就可以返回视图设计器加载程序完成加载，因为根设计器中，提供该视图，是由设计器加载程序创建的第一个对象之前。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fdb1-326">It is possible to return a view before the designer loader finishes loading because the root designer, which supplies the view, is the first object created by the designer loader.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fdb1-327">如果视图不可用，<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignSurface.BeginLoad%2A>引发异常。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fdb1-327">If a view is unavailable, <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignSurface.BeginLoad%2A> raises an exception.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7fdb1-328">视图技术的概念已过时。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fdb1-328">The notion of a view technology is obsolete.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fdb1-329">但是，它将保留在接口为根设计器向后兼容性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fdb1-329">But, it remains in the interfaces for root designers for backward compatibility.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fdb1-330">其用途隐藏的任何人使用<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignSurface>对象。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fdb1-330">Its use is hidden from anyone using <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignSurface> objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fdb1-331"><xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignSurface.View%2A>属性通过将受支持的技术传递回根设计器隐藏视图技术。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fdb1-331">The <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignSurface.View%2A> property hides view technologies by passing the supported technologies back into the root designer.</span></span>  
  
   
  
